data.description: Welcome to your new 4 bed, 3 bath home in Puyallup's quiet Summerview Terrace neighborhood! This beautiful home features vaulted ceilings, living room with a gas fireplace, dining room with access to the back deck, kitchen with tons of storage & and a pantry, Primary bedroom with an ensuite & walk-in closet, 2 additional bedrooms and bath on the upper level; and an additional bedroom, full bath, family room, utility room and access to the oversized 624 sq ft finished 2-car garage on the lower level. Outside, you'll find privacy & entertaining options with the large, fenced corner lot that backs to greenspace. Great location close to freeways, shopping, restaurants, parks, JBLM and more! Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity!
